72
00:05:05,699 --> 00:05:10,159
However awareness, utilization and development of your strengths

73
00:05:10,159 --> 00:05:12,039
is critical for adults too.

74
00:05:12,039 --> 00:05:16,469
This is not to say that you should forget about your weaknesses,

75
00:05:16,469 --> 00:05:17,400
of course not.

76
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:21,840
It is good to be aware of your own weaknesses and even try to improve them.

77
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:24,979
Especially, if they are holding you back from using your

78
00:05:24,979 --> 00:05:25,629
strengths.

79
00:05:25,629 --> 00:05:31,620
But it is strengths where real performance and growth comes from.

80
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:34,639
